%BB%A3ng-tr%E1%BA%A1ch-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-tu%C3%BD-h%E1%BA%ADu-mi%E1%BA%BFn-nhi%C3%AAn-h%E1%BB%AFu-t%C3%A1c/poem-Iq8VG8qwgWeEtu2Nhc0dkg">Sùng Nhượng trạch đông đình tuý hậu miến nhiên hữu tác - 崇讓宅東亭醉後沔然有作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-T%C6%B0-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/To%E1%BA%A1i-B%C3%ACnh-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-trung/poem-tJHck9MsosvMYKmtiH_shg">Toại Bình đạo trung - 遂平道中</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-T%C6%B0-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/author-k2nQ5fnr9ZRE2MDraIsNMQ">Nguyễn Tư Giản</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tr%C3%A1ng-du/poem-dLYEgwcQ7IbIIq24Mpcddw">Tráng du - 壯遊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/V%E1%BA%ADt-b%E1%BA%A5t-n%C4%83ng-dung/poem-Sh5A2yL6ck69H1c3amSMlg">Vật bất năng dung - 物不能容</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/author-vnduJD_TYrIrUDl9fyOqRw">Tuệ Trung thượng sĩ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
